---
import Brandmark from './Brandmark.astro';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t rule bg-bone-100/70">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 px-5 py-12 sm:grid-cols-[1.2fr_1fr_1fr]">
    <div>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="grid h-8 w-8 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-ink-800">
          <Brandmark size={16} />
        </span>
        <span class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-tightest text-ink-800">Nota</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-sm text-sm text-ink-400">
        AI personal-finance coach for Indonesia. Snap a receipt, see what you spent,
        hear a 60-second weekly recap. Built on the Xiaomi MiMo platform.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-300">
        Product
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-400">
        <li><a href="/scan"         class="hover:text-ink-800">Scan a receipt</a></li>
        <li><a href="/ledger"       class="hover:text-ink-800">Ledger & charts</a></li>
        <li><a href="/how-it-works" class="hover:text-ink-800">How it works</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about"        class="hover:text-ink-800">About Nota</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-ink-300">
        Quiet promises
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-400">
        <li>No account, no server database.</li>
        <li>Your receipts stay on this device.</li>
        <li>No ads, no upsell, no marketplace.</li>
        <li>Honest insights, in Bahasa.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t rule">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-start justify-between gap-2 px-5 py-5 text-xs text-ink-300 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
      <div>© {year} Nota · Made for the Xiaomi MiMo Orbit creator program.</div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-mono">
        <a href="https://platform.xiaomimimo.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="hover:text-ink-700">platform.xiaomimimo.com</a>
        <span class="opacity-40">·</span>
        <span>IDR · id-ID</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
